00:37:55,100 --> 00:37:57,400
ANGELA, WE REALLY SHOULD
BE GETTING YOU HOME.

671
00:37:57,600 --> 00:37:58,100
I'LL TAKE HER.

672
00:37:58,400 --> 00:38:00,400
NO, NO, NO.
YOU STAY, RELAX.

673
00:38:00,600 --> 00:38:01,000
ENJOY YOURSELF.

674
00:38:01,200 --> 00:38:03,200
YOUR FAVORITE SHOW
WILL BE COMING ON.

675
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:06,000
BESIDES, WE HAVE
SOMETHING TO DISCUSS.

676
00:38:06,200 --> 00:38:08,900
A CERTAIN PERSON'S
BIRTHDAY.

677
00:38:08,900 --> 00:38:10,500
OH, I SEE.

678
00:38:10,700 --> 00:38:12,000
TV announcer: AND THERE'LL BE
ANOTHER EPISODE

