696
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:55,100
BUT ENOUGH FROM ME.
LET'S JOIN THE ABBOTTS

697
00:38:55,300 --> 00:38:57,700
IN CAMDEN VILLAGE.

698
00:39:15,600 --> 00:39:18,000
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

699
00:39:19,400 --> 00:39:21,800
[RADIO STATIC]

700
00:39:22,200 --> 00:39:23,400
OH.

701
00:39:23,600 --> 00:39:26,100
THANK YOU, SWEETIE.

702
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:31,400
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU,

703
00:39:31,600 --> 00:39:33,100
BUT LET'S GO OUTSIDE.

704
00:39:33,300 --> 00:39:36,300
OH, SWEETIE, I'D LOVE TO,
BUT I'M REALLY LATE.

705
00:39:36,500 --> 00:39:39,000
WHAT'S YOUR RUSH?

706
00:39:39,500 --> 00:39:40,300
SURGERY.

707
00:39:40,500 --> 00:39:42,200
THERE WAS THAT ELEVATOR
DISASTER DOWNTOWN.

708
00:39:42,400 --> 00:39:43,700
IT WAS ON THE NEWS
LAST NIGHT.

709
00:39:43,900 --> 00:39:45,900
