00:39:48,500 --> 00:39:49,400
THE NON-UNION WORKERS.

712
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:51,600
JUST MONSTERS.
YOU KNOW, THAT BUILDING,

713
00:39:51,800 --> 00:39:53,100
IT'S RIGHT NEXT DOOR
TO WHERE YOU WORK.

714
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:55,200
CAN YOU IMAGINE IF YOU
HAD BEEN IN THERE?

715
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:57,100
IT'S NOT EVEN WORTH
THINKING ABOUT.

716
00:39:57,300 --> 00:39:58,100
ANYWAY,
I HAVE AN AMPUTATION

