718
00:40:01,300 --> 00:40:02,400
SHE'S VERY YOUNG.

719
00:40:02,600 --> 00:40:03,300
IT'S VERY SAD.

720
00:40:03,500 --> 00:40:05,400
ANYWAY, WISH ME LUCK.

721
00:40:05,600 --> 00:40:08,300
I'LL CROSS MY FINGERS
FOR YOU.

722
00:40:46,400 --> 00:40:48,600
[BRAKES SQUEAL]

723
00:40:48,800 --> 00:40:51,200
UH, EXCUSE ME.
HI. EXCUSE ME.

724
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:53,100
MAY I HELP YOU?

725
00:40:53,300 --> 00:40:53,600
OH, UH...

