00:40:53,800 --> 00:40:56,800
YES. I'M LOOKING FOR MY WIFE,
NURSE BURBANK.

727
00:40:58,100 --> 00:40:58,600
IT'S VERY IMPORTANT.

728
00:40:58,800 --> 00:41:01,200
I'M AFRAID THAT
THAT'S NOT POSSIBLE.

729
00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:02,500
SHE'S IN PRE-OP.

730
00:41:02,700 --> 00:41:04,100
SURE.

731
00:41:04,300 --> 00:41:06,000
OK, FINE.

732
00:41:06,200 --> 00:41:07,600
CAN YOU PASS ALONG A MESSAGE?

733
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:08,400
I'LL TRY.

734
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:10,300
CAN YOU TELL HER
I HAD TO GO TO FIJI

735
00:41:10,500 --> 00:41:12,100
AND THAT I'LL CALL HER
WHEN I GET THERE?

736
00:41:12,300 --> 00:41:15,000
WHEN YOU--
WHEN YOU GET TO FIJI?

737
00:41:15,300 --> 00:41:15,900
YOU GOT IT.

738
00:41:16,100 --> 00:41:18,600
FINE. I'LL TELL HER.

739
00:41:18,600 --> 00:41:21,100
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

740
00:41:46,600 --> 00:41:47,700
SORRY.

741
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:50,300
IT'S OK.

742
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:58,300
HE'S HERE.

743
00:41:58,800 --> 00:42:01,700
Meryl: I KNOW, I KNOW.
SHH, SHH, SHH.

744
00:42:02,100 --> 00:42:04,300
SCALPEL.

745
00:42:06,100 --> 00:42:08,400
AHEM.

746
00:42:09,200 --> 00:42:12,000
I'M NOW MAKING
MY PRIMARY INCISION

747
00:42:13,300 --> 00:42:15,900
JUST ABOVE THE RIGHT KNEE.

748
00:42:17,600 --> 00:42:19,900
[LOUD CLANG]

749
00:42:22,100 --> 00:42:23,000
NICELY DONE.

750
00:42:23,200 --> 00:42:26,000
THIS ISN'T
GOING TO BE PRETTY.

751
00:42:26,100 --> 00:42:28,700
IT'S JUST
BEAUTIFUL.

752
00:42:28,700 --> 00:42:30,100
BEAUTIFUL JOB.

753
00:42:30,300 --> 00:42:33,300
I'LL JUST LET SOMEONE ELSE
TIDY UP HERE.

